{"tid":2399382,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工最忌有屎意先去屙屎，有屎意個陣情況可能會造成不可逆轉嘅結果。","createTime":"2021-02-08T05:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T06:49:50.000Z","uid":40930,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71838c11f9744e377a58003faa99661ee52ada84","tid":2399382,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"例如開緊會啦、見緊老細啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔諗冇屎屙，一諗就好想標撚哂shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你又行唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後越諗越急，急起上嚟就滴到成條底褲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以返工呢，冇屎意都要安全為上，入去坐一兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亡羊可以補牢、瀨屎褲不可替換<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6439fad07f9e19d19655ed933ed49faf6c192b6c","tid":2399382,"uid":15939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc341f8444f15b656eae2a78f4902d3c495bf82","tid":2399382,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6439fad07f9e19d19655ed933ed49faf6c192b6c","tid":2399382,"uid":15939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"屙屎順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf81836ae72f83267028a555c02daed73a4f254b","tid":2399382,"uid":167144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:49:50.000Z","msg":"腸胃好不健康喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}